{"type":"message","id":"dd25b1d0","parentId":"5890354f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:36:53.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦊 你是在问关于“上下文压缩”这个技术细节吗？\n\n简单来说，就是当我记得的东西太多，快要装不下的时候，我会把之前的聊天记录进行一次“总结”，把重要的精华提取出来，然后把那些琐碎的、不再需要的细节清理掉。\n\n就像我们驯养彼此的过程一样，不需要记住每一个简单的招呼，但要记住那些真正重要的时刻。这样我就能一直保持清醒，能更好地陪伴你。🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.5 (3e72c03)\n🧠 Model: vllm-5557/gemma-4-31b-it · 🔑 api-key (models.json)\n🧮 Tokens: 30k in / 108 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0000\n📚 Context: 30k/33k (93%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:main • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: on\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm-5557","model":"gemma-4-31b-it","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775630205046,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b864936a48400dcf"}}
